1.) Copy the CSS code below to the wiki page at "wiki/index.php/MediaWiki:Common.css"
2.) Copy Extension to "extensions/UOItems" in your wiki folder
3.) Copy art.mul, artidx.mul und hues.mul to "extensions/UOItems/dataFiles"
4.) Add -> require_once("extensions/UOItems/uoItems.php"); <- to the end of your LocalSettings.php

---------------------------------------------------------------------
